Images of running project are in ProjectPrintScreen

Delete _chk folder in app folder (app/_chk) to remove Spark offsets and state.

Start containers (start terminal in project location):
podman machine start
podman-compose down
podman-compose up -d

Create kafka topics commands (after containers are UP):
podman exec -it kafka /opt/kafka/bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --topic comments_raw --partitions 3 --replication-factor 1
podman exec -it kafka /opt/kafka/bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --topic comments_scored --partitions 3 --replication-factor 1
podman exec -it kafka /opt/kafka/bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --topic toxic_alerts --partitions 3 --replication-factor 1
podman exec -it kafka /opt/kafka/bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list

Start spark consumer:
podman exec -it spark /opt/spark/bin/spark-submit --master spark://spark:7077 /opt/app/app/spark_stream.py

Start consumer alert command:
podman exec -it spark python3 /opt/app/app/consumer_alerts.py

Start producer command:
podman exec -it spark python3 /opt/app/app/producer.py